v1.1.1 - small balance changes

New Content:
+ 3 New Index Tiers

Changes:
+ Added more descriptive description to then 'Obelisk' furnace.
+ Adds an 'Enchants Offline' subheader within the Enchanter.
+ Made crystal comets despawn after 5 minutes.
+ Added a few new admin commands.
+ Added build credits for each submitter item
+ Add a global giveitem admin command, and confirmation when sent. Use ProfileStore messagehandler to handle this.
+ $/min and $/sec are now under ore limit
+ Items that you can only obtain once will complete all index entries underneath their tier (example: shiny mvp completes mvp, shiny mythic rebirth complete all rebirth entries)
+ You can now hover over items in the enchanter to see what their stats are.
+ Special Items and Secrets are no longer shown in your Index. However, if you own one, it will show, and contribute to the index.

Bug Fixes:
+ Helio-grader conveyor now moves ore.
+ Hoarded Treasure weird hitbox fix
+ Crystal Comets now despawn after 5 minutes.
+ Enchanter no longer says "no refunds" when cancelling.
+ Multiple secrets of the same type can now appear in the Enchanter
+ Updated description of the Candy Bomb to reflect longer ore lifetime
+ People that do not own the Rebirth IV badge (and are rebirth 4+) have been awarded it
+ Crystal Comets are now crystal shaped (not crate shaped), and float up and down

Balance Changes:
+ Ore Shrinker now shrinks ore by 15%, as opposed to the original 2.5%
+ Obelisk Furnace no longer looks for 'Red' ore, and now looks for 'Neon' ore
+ Alien Crate now costs 1Sp, as opposed to 50Sp
- Chartreuse Collider can now only upgrade ore up to 250Qn
